{"tid":549591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[紙老虎]俄戰機遭敍反抗軍擊落 機師拒被俘遭槍殺","createTime":"2018-02-03T18:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T16:35:57.000Z","uid":132859,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"78adaa6280881f8edb1d9e7b7eb8518234e7e0e9","tid":549591,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:29:30.000Z","msg":"一架俄羅斯戰機在敍利亞執行任務時，被反抗軍擊落，機師雖然及時彈射逃生，但著地後被反抗軍殺死。俄國防部證實有機師在敍利亞被殺。<br />\n<br />\n俄國的蘇25戰機是在周六於伊德利卜省（Idlib）被擊落，美聯社引述敍利亞反抗軍一名成員指，當時打算活捉俄國機師，但對方不斷反抗，又用手槍向反抗軍開火，結果他被射殺。<br />\n<br />\n俄國防部就表示機師在戰機被擊落後，彈射逃生落入聖戰組織「勝利陣線」（al-Nusra Front）的陣地，「機師與恐怖分子戰鬥時被殺」。而俄羅斯國營傳媒塔斯社就引述國防部消息指，俄軍後來在戰機被擊落的地點發動空襲，殺死30名敵對武裝分子。<br />\n<br />\n另外，5名土耳其士兵周六駕坦克在敍北阿夫林（Afrin）執行任務時，亦都遇襲死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180204&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57790189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180204%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57790189&d=pxqjvrwE%2Fn6xDQDs0E9K2Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=fd0bce57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180204%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57790189&h=df9f2242\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180204&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57790189</a>"},{"pid":"40495c42e2b3180df7954f9c7d035b4264139200","tid":549591,"uid":104443,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:30:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">士可殺      不可辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"73924b84df9a1083c83296cc1595cac7939fb541","tid":549591,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T18:35:46.000Z","msg":"Liveleak有冇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502283aa70e777de495a0592a2858808a33a35a0","tid":549591,"uid":62916,"like":